Revo Uninstaller Pro

Revo Uninstaller – innovative freeware uninstall utility. Uninstall, delete, remove programs and solve uninstalling problems. Revo Uninstaller is a much faster and more powerful alternative to “Windows Add or Remove Programs” applet! With its advanced and fast algorithm, Revo Uninstaller analyzes an application’s data before uninstall and scans after you uninstall an application.

• Auto Start Manager – Stop programs that start automatically on Windows startup; speed up loading of Windows!
• Windows Tools Manager – Handy and useful tools bundled with every version of Windows; easily find useful system tools and options!
